transcripts: This is the Breville Gourmet rice cooker. It actually cooks 10 cupsof uncooked rice in it and it will shut itself off so you don't have to worry about it. Another great thing is that it's got these stackable steamers so you can cook your vegetables and your fish or poultry at the same time as cooking your rice and of course it's got the non-stick both so it's so easy to clean. Another Innovation by Breville.
